    { "type": "row", "id": 200, "title": "Faro RUM ingestion flow", "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 21 } },
    {
      "id": 201, "type": "text", "title": "Flow",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "options": { "mode": "markdown", "content": "**Path:** Browser (Faro SDK) → **ALB** `/faro` → **faro-proxy** (nginx :8080, strips `/faro`) → **Alloy** `faro.receiver` :12347 `/collect` → **Loki** (logs, `job=faro`) + **Tempo** (client spans). Panels below trace each hop: ALB→faro target (CloudWatch) → receiver throughput/latency (Prometheus `faro_receiver_*`, job `alloy`) → events landing in Loki." }
    },
    {
      "id": 202, "type": "timeseries", "title": "Faro edge — ALB→target requests & HTTP codes",
      "datasource": { "type": "cloudwatch", "uid": "cloudwatch" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0 } },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right" } },
      "targets": [
        { "refId": "A", "namespace": "AWS/ApplicationELB", "metricName": "RequestCount", "statistic": "Sum", "dimensions": { "LoadBalancer": "app/k8s-public-f8655bfb7e/78080c3d6ec33605", "TargetGroup": "targetgroup/k8s-monitori-faroprox-25fb7e8eec/1717058bc4ff459b" }, "matchExact": true, "label": "requests" },
        { "refId": "B", "namespace": "AWS/ApplicationELB", "metricName": "HTTPCode_Target_2XX_Count", "statistic": "Sum", "dimensions": { "LoadBalancer": "app/k8s-public-f8655bfb7e/78080c3d6ec33605", "TargetGroup": "targetgroup/k8s-monitori-faroprox-25fb7e8eec/1717058bc4ff459b" }, "matchExact": true, "label": "2xx" },
        { "refId": "C", "namespace": "AWS/ApplicationELB", "metricName": "HTTPCode_Target_4XX_Count", "statistic": "Sum", "dimensions": { "LoadBalancer": "app/k8s-public-f8655bfb7e/78080c3d6ec33605", "TargetGroup": "targetgroup/k8s-monitori-faroprox-25fb7e8eec/1717058bc4ff459b" }, "matchExact": true, "label": "4xx" },
        { "refId": "D", "namespace": "AWS/ApplicationELB", "metricName": "HTTPCode_Target_5XX_Count", "statistic": "Sum", "dimensions": { "LoadBalancer": "app/k8s-public-f8655bfb7e/78080c3d6ec33605", "TargetGroup": "targetgroup/k8s-monitori-faroprox-25fb7e8eec/1717058bc4ff459b" }, "matchExact": true, "label": "5xx" }
